reviewText:
This DVD set is ok, I would have been disappointed if  had paid $100.00 for this program, The reason for this purchase was to learn a little about the auction chant before I took an auction class...

The DVD advised you to know the product you were bidding on, know ahead of time what is the most you will bid on an item before the auction starts,  talk to the auctioneer and develop a re-pore, so the auctioneer will notice you more during an auction, What to do if you open a auction company...
